pros: This frame stands out for its rustic looking appeal, and users love the natural look

product_meta.title: PRINZ Homestead 8-Inch by 10-Inch Rustic Frame in Distressed Finish, Gray
product_meta.description: Size:8x10| Color:Distressed GrayBring warmth, texture and casual charm to your photo display with this 8-by-10 rustic picture frame from the Homestead collection. Designed to evoke the feeling of warm, woodsy cabins and cozy, coastal cottages, this hand-distressed picture frame keeps your décor down to earth. The contemporary gray coloring makes it work well in more modern design styles, too. It holds a single 8-by-10 photograph and measures 11.1 by 13.1 inches by 0.8 inches deep overall. Display it horizontally or vertically on a tabletop, desktop or wall.
feature_bullets: Stylish, Rustic Design – Finished in a down-to-earth, hand-distressed gray, this attractive rustic photo frame brings a casual, charming vibe to your environment
Versatile Display Options – Designed to be displayed either vertically or horizontally on the wall or tabletop; Features wall hangers and a two-way easel
A Great Centerpiece – Displays a single 8-inch by 10-inch photograph so it makes a splash in a group of photos or on a gallery wall; Overall dimensions: 11. 1 by 13. 1 inches
High-Quality Materials – Constructed from durable, MDF and long-lasting hardware so it stays on display for years to come
Multiple Options Available – Mix and match sizes and colors with the PRINZ Homestead collection of rustic frames; Comes in multiple colors and sizes
